'''IsoBuster''' is a utility for CD and DVD data recovery.<ref>{{cite web |title=Recover file data from DVD, CD, BD and HD DVD discs (data rescue software) |url=http://www.isobuster.com/isobuster.php |publisher=Smart Projects |accessdate=2007-01-15}}</ref> All CD and DVD formats are supported, including [[HD DVD]] and [[Blu-ray Disc|Blu-Ray]]. It has the ability to access "deleted" data on multi-session [[CD-R]] and [[DVD-R]] discs, and allows users to access disc "images" in many formats (including [[ISO image|ISO]], BIN and NRG) and to extract files in the same way that they would from a [[ZIP (file format)|ZIP archive]].
'''IsoBuster''' is a utility for CD and DVD data recovery.<ref>{{cite web |title=Recover file data from DVD, CD, BD and HD DVD discs (data rescue software) |url=http://www.isobuster.com/isobuster.php |publisher=Smart Projects |accessdate=2007-01-15}}</ref> All CD and DVD formats are supported, including [[HD DVD]] and [[Blu-ray Disc|Blu-Ray]]. It has the ability to access "deleted" data on multi-session [[CD-R]] and [[DVD-R]] discs, and allows users to access disc "images" in many formats (including [[ISO image|ISO]], BIN and NRG) and to extract files in the same way that they would from a [[ZIP (file format)|ZIP archive]].
Produced by Smart Projects (founded at 1995 by Peter Van Hove) in Belgium.
